<TITLE> RAB arrests DCC engineer Faruk </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka,Sep29(bdnews24.com)RAB on Tuesday captured superintendent engineer of Dhaka City Corporation M Faruk Aziz on charges of threatening Dhaka City Corporation chief engineer Brig Gen Abdul Kader with death. Faruk Aziz was suspended on Sunday for his reported death threat at gunpoint to the senior army official deputed to the engineering division of the DCC reportedly over filling up the vacant post of additional engineer, for which Aziz is an aspirant. RAB-3 commander Lt Col Mamun Mahmud Firoj Chowdhury told bdnews24.com that they had detained Faruk Aziz at Shekhertek of the capital's Shaymoli area around 8pm on Tuesday. He is being quizzed under RAB custody, he said. Earlier, upon a written complaint, DCC mayor Sadeque Hossain Khoka formed a probe body into the incident after suspending Faruk Aziz temporarily. bd
